ey Cryptography II.- Generalized Identity Based and Broadcast Encryption Schemes.- Speeding Up the Pollard Rho Method on Prime Fields.- Sufficient Conditions for Intractability over Black-Box Groups: Generic Lower Bounds for Generalized DL and DH Problems.- OAEP Is Secure under Key-Dependent Messages.- Analysis of Stream Ciphers.- Cryptanalysis of Sosemanuk and SNOW 2.0 Using Linear Masks.- A New Attack on the LEX Stream Cipher.- Breaking the F-FCSR-H Stream Cipher in Real Time.